        "name": "Wave Spiral",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You dip and spin, unleashing a wide whirlpool of water. Make an Athletics check to Trip each creature standing on the ground in a 10-foot emanation. These attacks all count toward your multiple attack penalty, but the penalty doesn\u2019t increase until after you make all the attacks.",
